metadata.name: Light from Heaven
metadata.description:
Ever wanted to repel 150+ feet down into a cave, trek through knee deep mud and witness the light from heaven emerging from above? Well, the Goa Jomblang cave in Java, Indonesia offers that exact type of experience.

Only at a certain time of day the sun is at the perfect angle to shine light beams through from above, giving the cave an out of this world feel.

Camera: Sony Alpha 7 IV
Location: Goa Jomblang cave in Java, Indonesia
Edition: 1/1
Year: 2022
Photographer: Dennis Schmelz
License: Extended Editorial
Dimensions: 4440 × 5550
